data.description: NEW PRICE! Step into history with this Darling 1910 Craftsman Bungalow with original touches and moody gothic feels! 3 beds, 1 bath, and a spacious fenced yard for all your dreams to bloom. Covered parking in front and back with a separate alley entrance. Discover endless possibilities with a potential office and loft space in the attic. New roof , electrical,  updated bathroom, plumbing, and exterior paint. Situated just minutes away from bustling downtown shops, restaurants, and entertainment. The proximity to local businesses, universities, hospitals and employment hubs makes this home appealing to investors or first-time home buyers! Easy access to major highways, public transportation, making daily commutes a little easier.  Here's your canvas to craft a story as unique as you are!
